  "description": "<p><strong>随着Google Glass的发布，以及苹果、三星等公司正在开发的智能手表项目，可穿戴计算设备已经成为了一个热门话题。日前，摩托罗拉开发了一款专业级头戴式设备，以此证明，可穿戴计算设备的用户不仅仅局限于大众消费者。</strong>该产品旨在解决执法部门和其他公共安全部门对穿戴计算设备的需求。摩托罗拉解将这款设备称为“HC1头戴式计算机”。用户可以通过语音和头部动作控制HC1。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eac31e6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244722.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E7%BD%97%E6%8B%89%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E5%A4%B4%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%88%96%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244722.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E7%BD%97%E6%8B%89%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E5%A4%B4%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%88%96%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244722.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E7%BD%97%E6%8B%89%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E5%A4%B4%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%88%96%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244722.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E7%BD%97%E6%8B%89%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%BA%A7%E5%A4%B4%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87+%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%88%96%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://r